Titolo: Jump Force

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Jump Force is a Japanese  crossover fighting game developed by Spike Chunsoft and published by Bandai Namco Entertainment featuring characters from various manga series featured in Shueisha's Weekly Sh≈çnen Jump anthology in celebration of the magazine's 50th anniversary. The game was released on February 15, 2019 for Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One, and a Nintendo Switch port was released worldwide on August 28, 2020.On November 10, 2021, Bandai Namco announced the discontinuation of the game. Its delisting from digital stores along with all of its downloadable content is set for February 8, 2022, followed by the shutdown of its online servers on August 24, 2022.